Description:
    Generates an implementation of a tour component. A tour is managed in the
    CMS. It has an object class "Tour" and an object class "TourStep". Each tour
    consists of a tour object and its steps defined as children below the tour. Each step again can
    be composed with widgets right on the tour page.

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:tour`
    `rails generate cms:component:tour --example`

    CMS: obj_class Tour
           attribute headline (string)

         obj class TourStep
           attribute headline (string)
           attribute content (html)
           attribute show_in_navigation (enum)
           attribute sort_key (string)